    "All member and connection design is to be in accordance with latest version of the American Institute of Steel Construction (AISC) Specification for Structural Steel Buildings and the AISC Specification for Structural Joints using ASTM A325 or A490 bolts as found in the AISC Steel Construction Manual (SCM).",
